com.github.kvnxiao.kommandant.utility

Class StringSplitter

  • com.github.kvnxiao.kommandant.utility.StringSplitter

  • public class StringSplitter

    As of Kotlin 1.10, there is still some performance overhead in splitting strings by a literal. As such, string splitting in Java is currently still more performant than in Kotlin.
